    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1898-11-21T15:51:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1898-11-21T15:51:00-05:00" n="841"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d841">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Day</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">United States Peace Commission</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Paris</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date ana="#date_imprecise-inferred-from-document-content"
                            calendar="gregorian" when="1898-11-21T21:00:00+00:09">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 21, 1898</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 26.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>We presented this afternoon our proposal as telegraphed you in our No. 24. We
                    expressed expectation of American Commissioners that <pb facs="1054" n="958"
                        xml:id="pg_958"/> final and definite answer be given not later than 28th
                    instant. Also submitted answer to Spanish contention as to the construction of
                    protocol. They said we should have answer on Wednesday.</p>
                <closer>
                    <dateline rendition="#left">
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1898-11-21T21:00:00+00:09">Monday evening,
                            9</date>.</dateline>
                    <lb/>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Day.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
